         <abstract>
            <p> The miracle of St Mary and  Isaac has been transmitted in two variant miracle versions. To disambiguate, two CAe IDs <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7150Miracle">LIT7150Miracle</ref> and <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7151Miracle">LIT7151Miracle</ref> have
               been created for each miracle versions.  
               </p>
            
